jibe.sdk.client.group
Class GroupInfo

java.lang.Object
  jibe.sdk.client.group.GroupInfo

public class GroupInfo
extends java.lang.Object

Container class, which holds information about a particular group-chat session, such as which members belong to the group. See ChatSessionService.getGroupChatSessionInfo(long).
